<p>n = a * b <br/>
假设 \(a\leq b\),则有 \(a\leq \sqrt{n}\), 每有一个a就有两个被除数.
</p></div>

</div>

<div id="outline-container-3" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="sec-3"><span class="section-number-2">3</span> Answer</h2>
