<div id="outline-container-1" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="sec-1"><span class="section-number-2">1</span> Problem</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-1">

<blockquote>

<p>If we list all the natural numbers below 10 that are multiples of 3 or 5, we get 3, 5, 6 and 9. The sum of these multiples is 23.
</p>
<p>
Find the sum of all the multiples of 3 or 5 below 1000.
</p>
</blockquote>


</div>

</div>

<div id="outline-container-2" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="sec-2"><span class="section-number-2">2</span> Solution</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-2">

<p>  可以直接遍历找出所有整除3或5的数，然后相加，需要 \(O\) (n)。但如果运用数学集合的概念,只要 \(O\) (1).
</p>
<p>
  基本思路:
</p><ol>
<li>所有被3整除数相加
       3 + 6 + &hellip; + 999 = 3 * (1 + 2 + &hellip; + 333)
</li>
<li>加上所有被5整除数
       5 + 10 + &hellip; + 995 = 5 * (1 + 2 + &hellip; + 199)
</li>
<li>减去被15整除的数
       15 + 30 + &hellip; + 995 = 15 * (1 + 2 + &hellip;+ 16)
</li>
</ol>



<p>
  其中(1 + 2 + &hellip; + n) = (1 + n) * n / 2;
</p>
<p>
  333 = floor(1000/3);
</p>
</div>

</div>

<div id="outline-container-3" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="sec-3"><span class="section-number-2">3</span> Answer</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-3">

<p>  233168
</p>
<p>
Source:<a href="http://sdrv.ms/1512RxX">C++</a>
</p></div>
</div>
]]></content>
